    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 5,
    "last_activity_date" : 1644688367,
    "last_edit_date" : 1644688367,
    "creation_date" : 1631515666,
    "answer_id" : 69158400,
    "question_id" : 60362018,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>It was a permission issue...\nAfter upgrading chrome this error was showing so I followed the below mentioned steps and it worked in my system.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>System Preferences</li>\n<li>Security &amp; Privacy</li>\n<li>Go to General tab</li>\n<li>Allow apps downloaded from:</li>\n<li>Select App Store and identified developers</li>\n<li>Click the lock to make changes.</li>\n<li>Enter your system password</li>\n<li>Click Open Anyway to confirm your intent to open or install the app.</li>\n</ol>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
