    "question_id" : 60362018,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>After updating to Mac OS Ventura 13.0 you are now required to go to System Settings &gt; Privacy &amp; Security. Scroll down to the Security section and you can see chromedriver there. Click on Allow Anyway (it will prompt for admin credentials).</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/KQwqo.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/KQwqo.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
