  "body" : "<p>I have recently upgraded my mac machine to OS Catalina(v 10.15.3). After this upgrade I am unable to launch the chrome driver using selenium.</p>\n\n<p>I am facing the below error when I run the selenium code to launch the chrome browser.</p>\n\n<p>\"“chromedriver” cannot be opened because the developer cannot be verified\".\n\"macOS cannot verify that this app is free from malware.\"</p>\n\n<p>Please help me!</p>\n"
